arts.ttl: Sam Surridge, Hany Mukhtar both score twice in first half to lead Nashville over Orlando City 5-1
arts.sum: Surridge used an assist from Mukhtar — his 10th — to score in the 3rd minute and give Nashville (15-8-5) the lead. Sam Surridge and Hany Mukhtar both had two goals by halftime to help Nashville SC breeze to a 5-1 victory over Orlando City on Saturday night.
